Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:05.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for giving you guys the runaround.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I really meant it when I said it was fun, though! Seriously!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:14.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Rurino-chan, wait! This is all too sudden!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:19.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But… look, you know what they say about nipping buds.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:24.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I figured I’d do it now before I… you know, make things worse…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,B-But!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.68,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If that’s the case, then why join the School Idol Club in the first place!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:34.26,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you have something you wanted to do!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.49,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That’s…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.91,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I wanted to… with Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:43.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.97,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…No, it’s nothing.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.07,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I should’ve known this wouldn’t…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.38,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rurino-chan.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:01.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I understand you enjoy being alone.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.87,Kaho,,0,0,0,,When I was really young, I was really frail,\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:08.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,so I would spend every day reading in my room.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.11,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And I still like reading, even now.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:13.11,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:17.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want to just keep living like that, because I wanted to blossom!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:29.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I think I’d rather not cause trouble for others…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:35.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You all had to interrupt practice because of me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:36.50,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m really sorry.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:43.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah, but well, we’re still in the same class, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.41,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If we could… um… stay friends…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I think I’d really appreciate that.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:53.34,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.34,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Please, just give it another chance!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:01:59.85,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Another chance…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.01,Kaho,,0,0,0,,One more time!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:05.11,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Come to the club room, just one more time!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Please!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wouldn’t you hate it if things ended this way!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Consider it a request from me as well, Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.86,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It might just be me, but…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:25.21,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I think there’s a difference between enjoying being alone and becoming isolated.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:26.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.13,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Please!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:33.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry you have to keep worrying about me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,N-No, that’s not what…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:36.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Alright, I understand.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.44,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Just…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Don’t force yourself to do anything for me, okay?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.15,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You don’t have to worry about me being alone.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.19,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Come now, Kaho-san.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:02.22,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.09,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.86,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I was very surprised to hear you suddenly left school on a bus.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:11.91,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I managed to smooth things over with the dorm mother, but…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:14.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:19.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.94,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what’s… going on?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:31.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Here.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.67,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s nice and warm.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:47.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s hard to fathom that Rurino-san harbored such a side of her…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.86,Kozue,,0,0,0,,From looking at her, I fully believed she was a cheerful, positive girl…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:56.04,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You truly can’t judge a book by its cover.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.39,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But to think she’d had that application of resignation on her this whole time.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.07,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I suppose that means that somewhere inside her,\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:07.07,Kozue,,0,0,0,,she’s always felt that doing this would be impossible for her…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.90,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san, could you come over here?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:21.02,Kozue,,0,0,0,,The sky is clear tonight, so the stars are quite visible.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:24.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Please, take a look through this telescope.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.16,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.04,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.79,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Whoa… Amazing…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I didn’t think there were this many stars I couldn’t normally see…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Hmhm, fascinating, isn’t it?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.16,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We will soon be on summer vacation, won’t we?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.70,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Since I’d received a self-research assignment,\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I thought I’d start on it right away.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:54.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oof…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.38,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Summer… homework…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:04.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s why I had this telescope taken out and sent here from home.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:09.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this isn’t school property? It’s yours?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:10.94,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Correct.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:16.55,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I can’t explain why, but I’ve always liked stargazing.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.83,Kozue,,0,0,0,,There are very few stars visible to the naked eye.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:26.00,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, the sky is always full of stars.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I believe that school idols are similar.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:35.35,Kozue,,0,0,0,,My goal is, naturally, to shine as brightly as the brightest first-magnitude star, though.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.28,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:42.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what star you want to be like?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.13,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Um, Kozue-senpai…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.05,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you something…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.54,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Of course.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This… isn’t enough to properly thank you for before, but…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:00.24,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’ve felt you’ve had something to say for a while.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.94,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand how Rurino feels at all.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But I realized something when I had time to think about it by myself.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:14.69,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I figured… I probably didn’t even try to understand.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I was only focused on how much I wanted new members for the club.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So much so that I only saw Rurino-chan as just a possible new member.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:28.27,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But each school idol is different…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Just like the stars.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,There’s no one out there that exists just to be a new member!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You’re right.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:43.14,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Next time, I’ll definitely talk to Rurino-chan properly!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:51.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And… thank you, Kozue-senpai, for always looking after me and always spoiling me!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.83,Kozue,,0,0,0,,W-What’s with the sudden thanks…?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And for the last time, I do not spoil you.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.82,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So, um…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:03.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,If you can, there’s something I could use your help with, Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Of course I can, but…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:10.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This isn’t me spoiling you, okay?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:15.15,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I simply have a responsibility as club president to hear out any request from my club members.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.38,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ehehe, thanks, Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:20.87,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:27.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I might not know what kind of star I want to be like yet, but!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:32.56,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I want to make up a big constellation in the sky together with everyone!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:36.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And to do that, we need Rurino-chan to be with us!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,
